        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Brown and build",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Brown the {{sausages-pork}} in a dry pan over medium heat, turning until coloured on all sides, about 5 minutes. Transfer to the slow cooker. Add the {{onion}}, {{garlic}}, {{carrot}}, {{tinned-tomatoes}}, {{tomato-puree}}, {{smoked-paprika}}, {{worcestershire-sauce}}, {{stock-chicken}}, {{bay-leaves}}, {{thyme-fresh}}, {{sea-salt-fine}}, and {{black-pepper}}. Stir around the sausages. Cook on low for 6 hours. Remove the {{bay-leaves}} and {{thyme-fresh}} sprigs. Taste and adjust seasoning.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
