      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sausage casserole is a British family dinner that works across all ages. The slow cooker version is built in ten minutes in the morning and needs nothing more before serving. Serve over mashed potato or with crusty bread. Any leftovers reheat well the next day.",
            "type": "text"
          }
